<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>World News, Today World News, Latest International News, World Breaking News, Trending News of World - Times of India</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>World News Today: Read the latest world news headlines, Current International breaking news world wide. In depth analysis and top news headlines world wide.</description><language>en-gb</language><lastBuildDate>2026-07-11T19:18:16+05:30</lastBuildDate><atom:link type="application/rss+xml" rel="self" href="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/rssfeeds/296589292.cms"/><copyright>Copyright:(C) Sat, 11 Jul 2026 19:18:16 IST Bennett Coleman &amp; Co. Ltd, http://in.indiatimes.com/policyterms/1554651.cms</copyright><docs>http://syndication.indiatimes.com/</docs><image><title>World News, Today World News, Latest International News, World Breaking News, Trending News of World - Times of India</title><url>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/507610.cms</url><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link></image><item><title><![CDATA[‘I’ll play for India’: Popular US streamer IShowSpeed makes bold offer to help nation qualify for 2030 FIFA World Cup]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132331427.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[IShowSpeed joked that he would play for India’s national football team and help the country qualify for the 2030 World Cup. The YouTuber made the comments during a livestream while watching Spain vs Belgium. He said he could play as a winger, striker or attacking midfielder. While FIFA rules make the idea unrealistic, his support drew attention from football fans.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/ill-play-for-india-popular-us-streamer-ishowspeed-makes-bold-offer-to-help-nation-qualify-for-2030-fifa-world-cup/articleshow/132331427.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/ill-play-for-india-popular-us-streamer-ishowspeed-makes-bold-offer-to-help-nation-qualify-for-2030-fifa-world-cup/articleshow/132331427.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-11T18:48:51+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sumit Roy</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132331407,imgsize-925528.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Pakistan claims 88 militants killed in ongoing Balochistan crackdown]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132331157.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Pakistan's security forces have killed eighty-eight militants in Balochistan since July fifth.  Operation Shaban involves the army and paramilitary forces targeting militant hideouts.  This operation began after coordinated attacks rocked the province on July fifth.  Militants killed nine police personnel and abducted eighteen others at a checkpoint.  Violence also struck a local tribe, killing five and abducting eleven individuals.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-claims-88-militants-killed-in-ongoing-balochistan-crackdown/articleshow/132331157.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-claims-88-militants-killed-in-ongoing-balochistan-crackdown/articleshow/132331157.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-11T18:24:42+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132331169,imgsize-1431673.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Indian-origin tech leader killed by husband in Georgia over domestic dispute, wounded son runs to neighbors for help]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132330293.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[In a shocking domestic violence incident in Georgia, a man is charged after allegedly shooting his son and killing his wife. The injured son sought refuge with neighbors while Sheetal Wrzesien, the victim, a tech leader, was lying dead inside the house. The husband was arrested and charged with felony murder.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/indian-origin-tech-leader-killed-by-husband-in-georgia-over-domestic-dispute-wounded-son-runs-to-neighbors-for-help/articleshow/132330293.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/indian-origin-tech-leader-killed-by-husband-in-georgia-over-domestic-dispute-wounded-son-runs-to-neighbors-for-help/articleshow/132330293.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-11T17:41:04+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132331431,imgsize-735605.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[US lawmaker Ro Khanna says Israeli settlers armed with US-made rifles detained him in West Bank]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132329915.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[US Representative Ro Khanna reported being detained by armed Israeli settlers.  The incident occurred while he was visiting a destroyed Palestinian village.  Israeli security forces eventually intervened and dispersed the settlers.  Khanna stated the trip strengthened his resolve for a presidential run.  He also criticized US support for Israel and called for action against alleged genocide.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-lawmaker-ro-khanna-says-israeli-settlers-armed-with-us-made-rifles-detained-him-in-west-bank/articleshow/132329915.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-lawmaker-ro-khanna-says-israeli-settlers-armed-with-us-made-rifles-detained-him-in-west-bank/articleshow/132329915.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-11T17:32:27+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132330154,imgsize-843576.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[British MP Rupert Lowe unveils hardline Pakistan policy amid Shabir Ahmed deportation row]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132328201.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/british-mp-rupert-lowe-unveils-hardline-pakistan-policy-as-islamabad-refuses-to-accept-shabir-ahmeds-deportation/articleshow/132328201.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/british-mp-rupert-lowe-unveils-hardline-pakistan-policy-as-islamabad-refuses-to-accept-shabir-ahmeds-deportation/articleshow/132328201.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-11T16:29:27+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132329154,imgsize-557989.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Why modern-day Viking Erling Haaland has a very 'English' name]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132328109.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/why-haaland-is-a-very-english-name-viking-roots-england-connection-and-the-surprising-story-behind-his-surname/articleshow/132328109.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/why-haaland-is-a-very-english-na