ump/articleshow/132323107.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/reports-israeli-intel-warn-us-of-irans-plot-to-assassinate-trump/articleshow/132323107.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-11T06:49:18+05:30</pubDate><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132323111,imgsize-50420.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Nato leaders discussed security in Turkiye, got revolvers as return gift]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132323017.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/nato-leaders-discussed-security-in-turkiye-got-revolvers-as-return-gift/articleshow/132323017.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/nato-leaders-discussed-security-in-turkiye-got-revolvers-as-return-gift/articleshow/132323017.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-11T06:17:56+05:30</pubDate><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132323020,imgsize-14458.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA["He’s just been completely crazy": Connor Murphy's friend reveals what happened when the cameras stopped rolling]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132322906.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Connor Murphy's close friend Austin Wayne says the late fitness influencer's controversial looksmaxxing persona was largely an act created for content. Remembering Murphy as calm, kind and genuine, Wayne urged people to stop chasing clout from his death and instead prioritize mental health, saying, "That's much more important than looksmaxxing."]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/hes-just-been-completely-crazy-connor-murphys-friend-reveals-what-happened-when-the-cameras-stopped-rolling/articleshow/132322906.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/hes-just-been-completely-crazy-connor-murphys-friend-reveals-what-happened-when-the-cameras-stopped-rolling/articleshow/132322906.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-11T05:52:00+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Barsha Dutta</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132322906,imgsize-176914.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Candace Owens erupts at Andrew Kolvet’s Erika Kirk defense, calls biblical comparison ‘blasphemous’ and ‘sick’]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132322958.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Candace Owens and TPUSA spokesman Andrew Kolvet are once again publicly fighting over Charlie Kirk’s legacy. The latest dispute began after Kolvet used a religious analogy to criticize conspiracy theories, prompting Owens to call the post “blasphemous.” The feud is tied to Owens’ ongoing criticism of the official narrative surrounding Kirk’s 2025 killing and her long-running conflict with Erika Kirk.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/candace-owens-erupts-at-andrew-kolvets-erika-kirk-defense-calls-biblical-comparison-blasphemous-and-sick/articleshow/132322958.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/candace-owens-erupts-at-andrew-kolvets-erika-kirk-defense-calls-biblical-comparison-blasphemous-and-sick/articleshow/132322958.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-11T05:59:00+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sumit Roy</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132322955,imgsize-830268.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA["Making millions of dollars posting absolute lies": Candace Owens' net worth draws attention after Laura Loomer demands demonetization over Charlie Kirk claims]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132322919.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Laura Loomer has called for Candace Owens to be demonetized, accusing her of profiting from content about Charlie Kirk's death and allegedly harassing his family. Owens rejected the criticism and hit back at Loomer on X. The dispute comes amid Owens' ongoing public feud with Ben Shapiro and Andrew Kolvet, who have also criticized her commentary surrounding Kirk's death and the claims she has continued to promote.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/making-millions-of-dollars-posting-absolute-lies-candace-owens-net-worth-draws-attention-after-laura-loomer-demands-demonetization-over-charlie-kirk-claims/articleshow/132322919.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/making-millions-of-dollars-posting-absolute-lies-candace-owens-net-worth-draws-attention-after-laura-loomer-demands-demonetization-over-charlie-kirk-claims/articleshow/132322919.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-11T05:31:00+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Barsha Dutta</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132322919,imgsize-93760.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Justin Trudeau makes TikTok dancing debut in Katy Perry’s ‘Watch It Burn’ video]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132320440.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Justin Trudeau made a surprise dancing appearance in Katy Perry's TikTok video.  The former Canadian Prime Minister joined the singer and her team for a brief moment.  This playful cameo promoted Perry's new song, Watch It Burn, during her tour.  The couple, linked since July 2025, has made several public appearances together.  Trudeau's unexpected participation garnered significant attention across social media platforms.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/justin-trudeau-makes-tiktok-dancing-debut-in-katy-perrys-watch-it-burn-video/articleshow/132320440.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/justin-trudeau-makes-tiktok-dancing-debut-in-katy-perrys-watch-it-burn-video/articleshow/132320440.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-11T02:00:38+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sumit Roy</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132320438,imgsize-670886.cms"/></item></channel></rss>